WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Ybrick' is a Workbench game in which you have to place bricks
in all the empty spaces of a rectangular shaped board. If that
sounds simple, there's one little catch: similar bricks must
never touch; if that happens, those bricks will explode and be
removed from the board.

  Another complication is that although you can place bricks
anywhere you want on the lowest row, on the upper rows, bricks
can only be placed on top of other bricks.

  Have fun!

